{
  "video_id": "4BZuWrdC-9Q",
  "title": "Own Your Behaviours, Master Your Communication, Determine Your Success | Louise Evans | TEDxGenova",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Hui chu Chen Reviewer: Queenie Lee"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 20786.0,
      "end_time": 25472.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to introduce you to these five chairs"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 25472.0,
      "end_time": 30244.0,
      "text": "because they are actually the real protagonists of my talk."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 37193.0,
      "end_time": 42742.0,
      "text": "what behaviors and attitudes we bring into the world in every moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 34680.0,
      "end_time": 37193.0,
      "text": "and the message is about"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30974.0,
      "end_time": 34680.0,
      "text": "They have a special message to give to all of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 43737.0,
      "end_time": 45740.0,
      "text": "Now, to show you what I mean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 45740.0,
      "end_time": 48826.0,
      "text": "I have a story to tell you from my personal life."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 48826.0,
      "end_time": 52392.0,
      "text": "And I was trying to build a stronger relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 52392.0,
      "end_time": 54393.0,
      "text": "with a very important person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 54393.0,
      "end_time": 58252.0,
      "text": "the daughter of my partner, 20-year-old daughter."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 58512.0,
      "end_time": 59755.0,
      "text": "To do that, I thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 59755.0,
      "end_time": 62926.0,
      "text": "\"Let&#39;s have a great evening out, just the two girls together.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 62926.0,
      "end_time": 67000.0,
      "text": "And I chose a special venue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 67390.0,
      "end_time": 69650.0,
      "text": "the Blue Note Jazz Club in Milan."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 70120.0,
      "end_time": 74520.0,
      "text": "That night, the Manhattan Transfer, which is my favorite jazz group,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 74520.0,
      "end_time": 75402.0,
      "text": "were playing."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 75402.0,
      "end_time": 78294.0,
      "text": "So, we meet, atmosphere is fantastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 78294.0,
      "end_time": 80000.0,
      "text": "We are getting on very well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 80100.0,
      "end_time": 81795.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 84475.0,
      "end_time": 87262.0,
      "text": "Being a baby boomer, loving the music,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 88508.0,
      "end_time": 91445.0,
      "text": "I thought, \"Well, is she liking it as much as I am?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 91445.0,
      "end_time": 94518.0,
      "text": "So in that moment, I just turned to look at her to check."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 95653.0,
      "end_time": 98823.0,
      "text": "And what did I see? I saw this."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 99893.0,
      "end_time": 101824.0,
      "text": "She was on her iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 103234.0,
      "end_time": 105815.0,
      "text": "Now, how to react?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 105816.0,
      "end_time": 107295.0,
      "text": "I had some choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 108750.0,
      "end_time": 109194.0,
      "text": "First choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 112904.0,
      "end_time": 116116.0,
      "text": "Excuse me. What is she doing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 116117.0,
      "end_time": 117319.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s on her iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 117319.0,
      "end_time": 119274.0,
      "text": "I mean, I spent all this time and money"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 119274.0,
      "end_time": 122346.0,
      "text": "thinking of a fantastic evening, I bring her here, and what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 122346.0,
      "end_time": 124399.0,
      "text": "After two minutes I take my eyes off her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 124399.0,
      "end_time": 125969.0,
      "text": "and she&#39;s on her phone?"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 125969.0,
      "end_time": 128566.0,
      "text": "I mean, what is wrong with this generation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 128566.0,
      "end_time": 131528.0,
      "text": "I mean, they got  the attention span of a fruit fly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 131528.0,
      "end_time": 134970.0,
      "text": "for God&#39;s sake."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 134980.0,
      "end_time": 135718.0,
      "text": "(Sighing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 138880.0,
      "end_time": 139867.0,
      "text": "Choice number two."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 143807.0,
      "end_time": 145557.0,
      "text": "This was a mistake."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 145557.0,
      "end_time": 147760.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 147760.0,
      "end_time": 148779.0,
      "text": "Why did I bring her here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 148779.0,
      "end_time": 152997.0,
      "text": "I mean, she&#39;s bored; she&#39;s not interested; she doesn&#39;t like the music."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 152997.0,
      "end_time": 156549.0,
      "text": "What was I thinking? I mean: Why should she like the music?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 156549.0,
      "end_time": 159567.0,
      "text": "I mean, this is stuff for baby boomers."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 160177.0,
      "end_time": 163459.0,
      "text": "She probably thinks she&#39;s spending the evening with a dinosaur."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 164249.0,
      "end_time": 165652.0,
      "text": "Oh, God!"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 166622.0,
      "end_time": 169258.0,
      "text": "Choice number three."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 172638.0,
      "end_time": 174918.0,
      "text": "Hold your horses."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 174918.0,
      "end_time": 177489.0,
      "text": "Count to ten. Take a deep breath."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 178249.0,
      "end_time": 180559.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t jump to conclusions."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 180559.0,
      "end_time": 182869.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t know what she is doing on her iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 182869.0,
      "end_time": 185310.0,
      "text": "So just relax.Take it easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 186710.0,
      "end_time": 188151.0,
      "text": "Have another drink."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 188151.0,
      "end_time": 190527.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 191277.0,
      "end_time": 193300.0,
      "text": "Choice number four."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 194991.0,
      "end_time": 197498.0,
      "text": "Now, you know, what&#39;s really important for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 197498.0,
      "end_time": 200880.0,
      "text": "is that this evening together is special,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 200880.0,
      "end_time": 204710.0,
      "text": "that she feels that after this evening, she can really open up to me;"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 204711.0,
      "end_time": 207510.0,
      "text": "she can feel safe with me, and that -"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 207510.0,
      "end_time": 210622.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m always an open door for her, that&#39;s what&#39;s really important for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 211332.0,
      "end_time": 213209.0,
      "text": "I just hope it&#39;s going to happen -"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 213210.0,
      "end_time": 214602.0,
      "text": "I just hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 216382.0,
      "end_time": 218462.0,
      "text": "Choice number five."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 223832.0,
      "end_time": 225867.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s important for her?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 225867.0,
      "end_time": 228642.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s going on in her world right now?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 229412.0,
      "end_time": 230838.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s important for her?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 230838.0,
      "end_time": 233420.0,
      "text": "I really would love to connect to her."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 233420.0,
      "end_time": 234562.0,
      "text": "What do I need to do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 235212.0,
      "end_time": 236432.0,
      "text": "(Sighing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 236432.0,
      "end_time": 239811.0,
      "text": "You know, I was having real problems trying to answer that question."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 239812.0,
      "end_time": 244560.0,
      "text": "And in that moment, she turned to me and she said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 245183.0,
      "end_time": 248112.0,
      "text": "\"Louise, did you know that this is the only Blue Note"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 248112.0,
      "end_time": 249922.0,
      "text": "in the whole of Europe?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 249922.0,
      "end_time": 253142.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s one in New York, and then there&#39;s two in Japan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 253142.0,
      "end_time": 255110.0,
      "text": "but this is the only one here in Milan."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 255110.0,
      "end_time": 257483.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s incredible; the Italians have got it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 257483.0,
      "end_time": 261185.0,
      "text": "And she said, \"Oh, and I&#39;ve looked up the Manhattan Transfer."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 261185.0,
      "end_time": 264941.0,
      "text": "Do you know that they&#39;ve been playing and singing together for 40 years?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 264942.0,
      "end_time": 266511.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s incredible!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 267421.0,
      "end_time": 270440.0,
      "text": "And she said, \"Also, look.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 270604.0,
      "end_time": 274614.0,
      "text": "She handed me her iPhone; she&#39;d sent a message out on Facebook;"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 274614.0,
      "end_time": 277751.0,
      "text": "it said, \"In the Blue Note in Milan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 278603.0,
      "end_time": 283373.0,
      "text": "with the Manhattan transfer and Louise, the best!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 286223.0,
      "end_time": 289102.0,
      "text": "Now, that was a close shave."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 289102.0,
      "end_time": 291193.0,
      "text": "I mean, I could&#39;ve really spoiled that."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 291194.0,
      "end_time": 295513.0,
      "text": "Because I could have sent her a disapproving look from this chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 296243.0,
      "end_time": 299883.0,
      "text": "And she could&#39;ve started telling herself about me, things about me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 299883.0,
      "end_time": 304920.0,
      "text": "like, Louise, she&#39;s controlling."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 304920.0,
      "end_time": 305794.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 305794.0,
      "end_time": 308115.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not easy to be around her."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 308115.0,
      "end_time": 310505.0,
      "text": "And that was not my intention at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 310505.0,
      "end_time": 313647.0,
      "text": "And in fact, she was completely engaged."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 313648.0,
      "end_time": 314702.0,
      "text": "She was there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 314702.0,
      "end_time": 319247.0,
      "text": "multitasking in her digital way, but she was enhancing our reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 319247.0,
      "end_time": 321394.0,
      "text": "So, in milliseconds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 321394.0,
      "end_time": 325333.0,
      "text": "I could have destroyed that beautiful moment that we were creating together."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 326413.0,
      "end_time": 329395.0,
      "text": "And this is what we are doing all the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 329395.0,
      "end_time": 334152.0,
      "text": "we are making choices about the behaviors that we bring into the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 334796.0,
      "end_time": 338375.0,
      "text": "And the choices that we make have a direct impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 338375.0,
      "end_time": 341405.0,
      "text": "on the conversations that we have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 341405.0,
      "end_time": 343979.0,
      "text": "the relationships that we form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 343980.0,
      "end_time": 346985.0,
      "text": "and the quality of our lives in general."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 347625.0,
      "end_time": 352815.0,
      "text": "So, what can we do at a practical level"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 352815.0,
      "end_time": 355650.0,
      "text": "to help us be more conscious about this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 355650.0,
      "end_time": 357610.0,
      "text": "Because they don&#39;t train us this in school."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 357610.0,
      "end_time": 360578.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not on the school curriculum - how to behave well, really."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 360579.0,
      "end_time": 362274.0,
      "text": "So, what can we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 362274.0,
      "end_time": 365532.0,
      "text": "The idea of the five chairs came to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 365532.0,
      "end_time": 371835.0,
      "text": "when I went and attended a nine-day course in nonviolent communication"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 371836.0,
      "end_time": 376325.0,
      "text": "with its late founder, Marshall Rosenberg, an extraordinary man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 376325.0,
      "end_time": 379327.0,
      "text": "who did so much for world peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 379327.0,
      "end_time": 381867.0,
      "text": "And after that, it sort of changed my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 381867.0,
      "end_time": 384537.0,
      "text": "After that, I decided that it was a message"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 384537.0,
      "end_time": 388347.0,
      "text": "that I needed to get into our workplaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 388347.0,
      "end_time": 390796.0,
      "text": "Workplaces where I spend most of my time"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 390797.0,
      "end_time": 395182.0,
      "text": "being a coach, a facilitator, and the trainer."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 395717.0,
      "end_time": 401645.0,
      "text": "And also, where we produce some of our most questionable behaviors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 401646.0,
      "end_time": 404277.0,
      "text": "sometimes toxic behaviors."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 404667.0,
      "end_time": 409691.0,
      "text": "So, the idea of the five chairs is to help us slow down"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 409691.0,
      "end_time": 413558.0,
      "text": "how we are behaving in every moment of our lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 413559.0,
      "end_time": 415332.0,
      "text": "and to analyze what&#39;s going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 415933.0,
      "end_time": 417655.0,
      "text": "So, what I would like to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 417655.0,
      "end_time": 422294.0,
      "text": "is look at the chairs more closely and explain them."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 422294.0,
      "end_time": 423832.0,
      "text": "The red chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 428323.0,
      "end_time": 431170.0,
      "text": "This is the jackal chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 431170.0,
      "end_time": 436607.0,
      "text": "I mean, jackals are incredibly clever, incredibly opportunistic animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 436607.0,
      "end_time": 439419.0,
      "text": "They always on the lookout to attack."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 440119.0,
      "end_time": 445778.0,
      "text": "And in fact, this chair here is the chair where we misbehave the most."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 446375.0,
      "end_time": 453300.0,
      "text": "In this chair we love to blame, to complain, to punish, to gossip;"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 453469.0,
      "end_time": 457798.0,
      "text": "but our supreme game  in this chair is to judge."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 458478.0,
      "end_time": 463178.0,
      "text": "And if you don&#39;t believe me, I invite you to go on a mental diet;"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 463751.0,
      "end_time": 469214.0,
      "text": "I invite you to spend one hour with some human beings"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 469801.0,
      "end_time": 473628.0,
      "text": "and see if you can do it without one single judgment"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 473629.0,
      "end_time": 475366.0,
      "text": "going through your mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 476139.0,
      "end_time": 477682.0,
      "text": "I mean, watch ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 477682.0,
      "end_time": 480439.0,
      "text": "Somebody walks in the door, we go: bzzzzzzzzz,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 481199.0,
      "end_time": 483995.0,
      "text": "I like, don&#39;t like, not really interested."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 484425.0,
      "end_time": 487100.0,
      "text": "And we don&#39;t know anything about them at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 487100.0,
      "end_time": 488994.0,
      "text": "So, this chair here"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 489964.0,
      "end_time": 491442.0,
      "text": "is a judging chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 491442.0,
      "end_time": 494507.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s actually another game that I love in this chair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 494507.0,
      "end_time": 497164.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the \"I&#39;m right\" game."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 497164.0,
      "end_time": 499680.0,
      "text": "And I used to do that all time, all the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 499680.0,
      "end_time": 502330.0,
      "text": "until my brother gave me some feedback."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 502330.0,
      "end_time": 505602.0,
      "text": "I used to do it with my mother because my mother likes to exaggerate."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 505602.0,
      "end_time": 507667.0,
      "text": "So she would say something like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 507668.0,
      "end_time": 511950.0,
      "text": "\"Oh yes, there were 30 people at the family gathering.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 512100.0,
      "end_time": 513712.0,
      "text": "And my job was to correct her."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 513712.0,
      "end_time": 517532.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m saying, \"No, Mom, they weren&#39;t 30, they were 13.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 518172.0,
      "end_time": 521241.0,
      "text": "So, I was the policewoman of the situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 522541.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524561.0,
      "text": "My brother touched me on the arm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 524561.0,
      "end_time": 529836.0,
      "text": "and he said, \"It doesn&#39;t matter,\" to which I reacted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 529836.0,
      "end_time": 533272.0,
      "text": "\"What do you mean it doesn&#39;t matter? Of course, it matters. She&#39;s wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 533272.0,
      "end_time": 535603.0,
      "text": "And she needs to be corrected for her own good.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 537549.0,
      "end_time": 540414.0,
      "text": "He touched me on the arm again, and he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 540414.0,
      "end_time": 543352.0,
      "text": "\"Do you want to be in a relationship with your mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 543352.0,
      "end_time": 546430.0,
      "text": "or do you want to be right?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 548192.0,
      "end_time": 549923.0,
      "text": "Big lesson."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 549923.0,
      "end_time": 550935.0,
      "text": "From then on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 550935.0,
      "end_time": 556362.0,
      "text": "I always looked upon my mother&#39;s exaggeration as a form of abundance."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 557682.0,
      "end_time": 560478.0,
      "text": "So, here in this chair, what we tend to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 560478.0,
      "end_time": 563381.0,
      "text": "is we tend to see what is wrong with other people"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 563381.0,
      "end_time": 564983.0,
      "text": "rather than what is right."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 564984.0,
      "end_time": 567282.0,
      "text": "Mother Teresa reminds us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 567282.0,
      "end_time": 572473.0,
      "text": "\"The more we judge people, the less time we have to love them.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 574334.0,
      "end_time": 577180.0,
      "text": "The next chair is the hedgehog chair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 577190.0,
      "end_time": 578190.0,
      "text": "the yellow chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 578190.0,
      "end_time": 580103.0,
      "text": "Now, the hedgehog -"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 580103.0,
      "end_time": 583127.0,
      "text": "When we behave like hedgehogs, we feel very vulnerable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 583127.0,
      "end_time": 589242.0,
      "text": "and we curl up, we protect ourselves against what we feel is an evil world."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 589652.0,
      "end_time": 594459.0,
      "text": "And what we do is we mercilessly judge ourselves in this chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 594459.0,
      "end_time": 599151.0,
      "text": "So we turn this chair, the red chair, on ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 599612.0,
      "end_time": 602216.0,
      "text": "And we say things like, \"I&#39;m not intelligent enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 602216.0,
      "end_time": 605314.0,
      "text": "I cannot do this. Nobody believes in me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 605714.0,
      "end_time": 607403.0,
      "text": "And we have certain fears,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 607403.0,
      "end_time": 614680.0,
      "text": "we have fears of being rejected, fears of disappointing, fears of failing."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 614493.0,
      "end_time": 616214.0,
      "text": "And we also play the victim."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 616214.0,
      "end_time": 620515.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s, \"Nobody cares for me, nobody loves me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 621425.0,
      "end_time": 623300.0,
      "text": "But in fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 623400.0,
      "end_time": 627105.0,
      "text": "when I use this in companies, and I ask managers, and I say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 627105.0,
      "end_time": 629749.0,
      "text": "\"Where do you spend the most of your time?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 630699.0,
      "end_time": 633694.0,
      "text": "Hardly anybody comes and sits here."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 633695.0,
      "end_time": 637732.0,
      "text": "Because it&#39;s quite difficult to admit our weaknesses sometimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 637732.0,
      "end_time": 639396.0,
      "text": "We need a lot of courage."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 639396.0,
      "end_time": 643144.0,
      "text": "And yet, we all suffer from self-doubt."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 643144.0,
      "end_time": 646224.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s really, what do we do without self-doubt?"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 647214.0,
      "end_time": 649195.0,
      "text": "Do we give up and give in?"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 650500.0,
      "end_time": 651491.0,
      "text": "Or do we say no?"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 651491.0,
      "end_time": 653646.0,
      "text": "I want to find the resources and grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 654387.0,
      "end_time": 657113.0,
      "text": "And Krishnamurti says something wonderful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 657114.0,
      "end_time": 660214.0,
      "text": "he says, \"The highest form of intelligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 660214.0,
      "end_time": 664803.0,
      "text": "is the ability to observe ourselves without judging.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 665993.0,
      "end_time": 668585.0,
      "text": "So, next chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 670845.0,
      "end_time": 673515.0,
      "text": "This is the meerkat chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 673515.0,
      "end_time": 676226.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know if you&#39;ve ever seen a meerkat."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 676226.0,
      "end_time": 680758.0,
      "text": "They are not many in Italy, but they are incredible."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 680758.0,
      "end_time": 682787.0,
      "text": "When they are on sentinel duty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 682787.0,
      "end_time": 686246.0,
      "text": "they can stay for one hour just like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 686246.0,
      "end_time": 689886.0,
      "text": "one hour moving their head and only their head."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 689886.0,
      "end_time": 691678.0,
      "text": "Incredibly vigilant."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 691678.0,
      "end_time": 694965.0,
      "text": "And when we are in this chair, this is what we do."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 694965.0,
      "end_time": 697327.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re mindful; we&#39;re very aware;"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 697327.0,
      "end_time": 700236.0,
      "text": "we are observant; we stop; we pause."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 700236.0,
      "end_time": 703980.0,
      "text": "We take a deep breath, and we&#39;re conscious."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 703980.0,
      "end_time": 707435.0,
      "text": "This is the WAIT chair. W-A-I-T."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 708600.0,
      "end_time": 712488.0,
      "text": "What am I thinking? What am I telling myself?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 713129.0,
      "end_time": 715608.0,
      "text": "So here we become very curious."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 715608.0,
      "end_time": 720205.0,
      "text": "If somebody is angry, instead of saying, \"For God sake: grow up, will you?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 720557.0,
      "end_time": 723936.0,
      "text": "We think, \"I wonder why that person is angry?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 723936.0,
      "end_time": 725858.0,
      "text": "And we feel interested."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 725858.0,
      "end_time": 727882.0,
      "text": "So this chair here is ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 729312.0,
      "end_time": 730622.0,
      "text": "When I think of Nietzsche,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 730622.0,
      "end_time": 732818.0,
      "text": "this is such an important quote for this chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 732818.0,
      "end_time": 737680.0,
      "text": "He says, \"You have your way; I have my way."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 737680.0,
      "end_time": 741831.0,
      "text": "As for the right way and the only way, it does not exist.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 742648.0,
      "end_time": 744719.0,
      "text": "So here we have a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 746259.0,
      "end_time": 749157.0,
      "text": "The red pill or the blue pill?"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 749157.0,
      "end_time": 751517.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the sliding door chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 751517.0,
      "end_time": 755132.0,
      "text": "And in this moment when we make the right choice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 755132.0,
      "end_time": 758544.0,
      "text": "we move into this successful living."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 759634.0,
      "end_time": 761230.0,
      "text": "Next chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 761813.0,
      "end_time": 764518.0,
      "text": "Here we go into the world of detect."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 764518.0,
      "end_time": 766337.0,
      "text": "Now, why detect?"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 766337.0,
      "end_time": 769987.0,
      "text": "Detect because we become detective of ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 769987.0,
      "end_time": 771814.0,
      "text": "like Sherlock Holmes of ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 771815.0,
      "end_time": 776443.0,
      "text": "We take a magnifying glass, and we look at our behaviors."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 776443.0,
      "end_time": 780127.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a beautiful chair because we become self-aware."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 780132.0,
      "end_time": 782516.0,
      "text": "We know who we are. We know what we want."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 782517.0,
      "end_time": 786160.0,
      "text": "We know where we&#39;re going. We&#39;re not afraid to speak our truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 786160.0,
      "end_time": 788856.0,
      "text": "But we also create our boundaries."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 788856.0,
      "end_time": 790976.0,
      "text": "We look after ourselves in this chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 790976.0,
      "end_time": 792642.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;re very very powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 792642.0,
      "end_time": 794449.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t give our power away."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 794569.0,
      "end_time": 796501.0,
      "text": "Here we give our power away."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 796501.0,
      "end_time": 799947.0,
      "text": "So here we grow, we become free."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 799947.0,
      "end_time": 802910.0,
      "text": "We come into our full power."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 802910.0,
      "end_time": 805880.0,
      "text": "We become assertive, but not aggressive."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 806530.0,
      "end_time": 812240.0,
      "text": "Aristotle said, \"Knowing yourself is the beginning of all wisdom.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 812240.0,
      "end_time": 815334.0,
      "text": "We can be here for our whole lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 815334.0,
      "end_time": 816901.0,
      "text": "Why the dolphin?"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 816901.0,
      "end_time": 821872.0,
      "text": "The dolphin because it&#39;s such a wonderful animal."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 821872.0,
      "end_time": 826310.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s playful; it&#39;s intelligent; it communicates beautifully."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 826310.0,
      "end_time": 827471.0,
      "text": "When I think of the dolphin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 827471.0,
      "end_time": 832150.0,
      "text": "I think of us at our very best as human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 833661.0,
      "end_time": 835671.0,
      "text": "So, next chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 841872.0,
      "end_time": 845229.0,
      "text": "This is the giraffe chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 846330.0,
      "end_time": 848183.0,
      "text": "Very beautiful chair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 849430.0,
      "end_time": 850759.0,
      "text": "very difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 850759.0,
      "end_time": 853332.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know if you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 853332.0,
      "end_time": 859613.0,
      "text": "but the giraffe has the biggest heart of all land animals;"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 859613.0,
      "end_time": 861123.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s that size."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 861123.0,
      "end_time": 864670.0,
      "text": "And not only does it have the biggest heart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 864670.0,
      "end_time": 867320.0,
      "text": "it also has the longest neck."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 867532.0,
      "end_time": 869831.0,
      "text": "So it has incredible vision."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 870261.0,
      "end_time": 873420.0,
      "text": "So when we are in this chair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 873420.0,
      "end_time": 878652.0,
      "text": "we are displaying empathy, compassion, and understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 879374.0,
      "end_time": 883514.0,
      "text": "And in this chair, we put our egos on the back burner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 884214.0,
      "end_time": 886224.0,
      "text": "and we listen to people."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 886224.0,
      "end_time": 890531.0,
      "text": "We hold people in our presence, and we care for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 892527.0,
      "end_time": 896612.0,
      "text": "Stepping into somebody else&#39;s shoes and understanding them"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 896612.0,
      "end_time": 899280.0,
      "text": "is a great act of generosity."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 900710.0,
      "end_time": 902903.0,
      "text": "Abraham Lincoln once said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 902903.0,
      "end_time": 907282.0,
      "text": "\"I don&#39;t like that man. I must get to know him better.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 908752.0,
      "end_time": 911723.0,
      "text": "So in this chair, it&#39;s an invitation"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 912504.0,
      "end_time": 914754.0,
      "text": "to look at other perspectives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 914754.0,
      "end_time": 917484.0,
      "text": "to embrace other realities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 917484.0,
      "end_time": 920134.0,
      "text": "to embrace diversity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 920134.0,
      "end_time": 922475.0,
      "text": "and to become tolerant."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 923445.0,
      "end_time": 928324.0,
      "text": "And the most important question in this chair is what is important"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 928324.0,
      "end_time": 930926.0,
      "text": "for him or her in front of me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 930927.0,
      "end_time": 936375.0,
      "text": "And the intention in this chair is to stay connected whatever happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 937365.0,
      "end_time": 939306.0,
      "text": "So these are the chairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 940386.0,
      "end_time": 942771.0,
      "text": "How do we translate this into daily life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 942772.0,
      "end_time": 945766.0,
      "text": "Well, you can imagine, if you go to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 946366.0,
      "end_time": 949232.0,
      "text": "maybe you can go, and you give a presentation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 949232.0,
      "end_time": 950742.0,
      "text": "and it goes really well."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 950743.0,
      "end_time": 954106.0,
      "text": "So you are here, thinking, \"Great, fantastic!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 954106.0,
      "end_time": 958300.0,
      "text": "Then, maybe you have a meeting and things go badly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 958300.0,
      "end_time": 960956.0,
      "text": "and we sink into these chairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 960956.0,
      "end_time": 966266.0,
      "text": "Now our challenge every day is to understand how to find the balance"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 966776.0,
      "end_time": 969987.0,
      "text": "between sitting here and sitting here."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 969987.0,
      "end_time": 973100.0,
      "text": "Because if we&#39;re sitting here, life is not that happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 974645.0,
      "end_time": 976818.0,
      "text": "But if we&#39;re sitting here, in these chairs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 976818.0,
      "end_time": 978886.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re more rational; we&#39;re more open;"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 978886.0,
      "end_time": 981824.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re more intelligent; we&#39;re more thoughtful."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 987750.0,
      "end_time": 990517.0,
      "text": "Something that really moved me very very deeply when I first read it"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 990517.0,
      "end_time": 995377.0,
      "text": "was this: Viktor Frankl, in his book Man&#39;s Search for Meaning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 995377.0,
      "end_time": 999876.0,
      "text": "said, \"Everything can be taken from man but one thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1000410.0,
      "end_time": 1003280.0,
      "text": "The last of human freedoms -"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1003280.0,
      "end_time": 1008341.0,
      "text": "to choose our attitude in any given set of circumstances.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1009200.0,
      "end_time": 1011236.0,
      "text": "This is so powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1011240.0,
      "end_time": 1015221.0,
      "text": "So when you next want to snap at your children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1015940.0,
      "end_time": 1018232.0,
      "text": "or argue with your partner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1018230.0,
      "end_time": 1021136.0,
      "text": "or punish someone at work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1021140.0,
      "end_time": 1023523.0,
      "text": "try and come into this chair here and think."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1024680.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1028759.0000000001,
      "text": "And if by chance, you end up in this chair -"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1028760.0,
      "end_time": 1030742.0,
      "text": "which very often happens -"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1031730.0,
      "end_time": 1035397.0,
      "text": "can we find the courage to say \"I&#39;m sorry\""
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1035400.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1037853.0000000001,
      "text": "and make everything right again?"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1038819.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1043801.9999999999,
      "text": "So, my invitation to you is to take these chairs home with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1044839.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1047186.9999999999,
      "text": "Play with them. Make them your own."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1047190.0,
      "end_time": 1050171.0,
      "text": "Teach them to your kids; they get this immediately."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1050170.0,
      "end_time": 1052715.0,
      "text": "Put five of them in the boardroom at work"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1052710.0,
      "end_time": 1055895.0,
      "text": "and watch how your meetings will improve."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 1055570.0,
      "end_time": 1060984.0,
      "text": "And the next time somebody presses one of your red buttons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 1061940.0,
      "end_time": 1067841.0,
      "text": "just think: five chairs, five choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 1069900.0,
      "end_time": 1075121.0,
      "text": "Can we all commit to making our homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 1075120.0,
      "end_time": 1079401.0,
      "text": "our workplaces, and this world a better place?"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 1080190.0,
      "end_time": 1082990.0,
      "text": "One behavior at a time."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 1084370.0,
      "end_time": 1085656.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 1085660.0,
      "end_time": 1088439.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}